   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d5248f86",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Attention Dilution — Phases 1 & 2 (Qwen3-1.7B / A100)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Today's deliverable:** complete Phase 1 + Phase 2. Phase 3 cells are included at the bottom but can be skipped.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Model:** `Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B` — 28 layers, 16 Q / 8 KV heads (GQA), d_model=2048, 32K context, qk-layernorm, untied embeddings.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Critical Qwen3 gotcha:** Qwen3 defaults to **thinking mode** — it emits a `<think>...</think>` block before answering. For interpretability we MUST disable this (it pollutes activations, breaks refusal detection, and bloats generations). We use `enable_thinking=False` everywhere.\n",
    "\n",
    "**A100 budget:** you can run the full sweep up to 16K context and use `use_attn_result=True` for clean per-head attribution. No cuts needed."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "418027c7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
